# MBA Design Rules

Generate UI/UX that looks professionally designed by humans, not AI.

## Critical Resources

| Resource | Path | Purpose |
|----------|------|---------|
| Design Tokens | `.mba-template/tokens/tokens.css` | ALL approved values |
| Sample Content | `.mba-template/content/sample-content.json` | Realistic placeholder data |
| Component Examples | `.mba-template/examples/` | Working HTML references |
| Anti-Patterns | `.mba-template/anti-patterns/ai-generated-tells.md` | What NOT to do |

---

## 1. Spacing (Use tokens.css)

**APPROVED VALUES ONLY:**
```
4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 20px, 24px, 32px, 40px, 48px, 64px, 80px, 96px
```

**FORBIDDEN:** 7px, 13px, 19px, 23px, or ANY value not listed above.

| Context | Values |
|---------|--------|
| Icon gaps | 4-8px |
| Button padding | 8-12px vertical, 16-24px horizontal |
| Card padding | 16-24px |
| Section spacing | 48-64px |
| Page margins | 16px (mobile), 24px (tablet), 32px (desktop) |

---

## 2. Colors (Use tokens.css)

**Use semantic tokens only.** Never invent hex colors.

| Role | Token | Usage |
|------|-------|-------|
| Text primary | `--color-text-primary` | Main content |
| Text secondary | `--color-text-secondary` | Supporting text |
| Background | `--color-bg-primary` | Page background |
| Interactive | `--color-interactive-primary` | Buttons, links |
| Success | `--color-status-success` | Positive feedback |
| Error | `--color-status-error` | Errors, destructive |
| Warning | `--color-status-warning` | Caution states |

**Contrast:** 4.5:1 minimum (body text), 3:1 (large text 18px+)

---

## 3. Typography

**Font:** System stack (`-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif`)

| Element | Size | Weight | Line Height |
|---------|------|--------|-------------|
| H1 | 32-48px | 700 | 1.1-1.2 |
| H2 | 24-32px | 600 | 1.2-1.3 |
| H3 | 20-24px | 600 | 1.3 |
| Body | 14-16px | 400 | 1.5-1.6 |
| Small | 12-14px | 400 | 1.4 |

**Line length:** 50-75 characters (`max-width: 65ch`)

---

## 4. Border Radius

**ONLY these 4 values:**
```
4px  - buttons, inputs, tags
8px  - cards, dropdowns
12px - modals, large panels
9999px - pills, avatars ONLY
```

**FORBIDDEN:** 16px+ on small elements, random values like 6px, 10px, 14px.

---

## 5. Icons

**NEVER generate SVG code.** Use icon libraries:

```html
<!-- Font Awesome (recommended) -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
<i class="fa-solid fa-user" aria-hidden="true"></i>

<!-- With accessible label -->
<button aria-label="Close"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
```

**Sizes:** 16px, 20px, 24px, 32px, 48px

---

## 6. Components

### Buttons
- **Primary:** Filled, brand color
- **Secondary:** Outlined/ghost
- **Danger:** Red, destructive actions
- **Sizes:** 32px (sm), 40px (md), 48px (lg) height

### Inputs
- Height: 40px default
- Padding: 12-16px horizontal
- States: default, hover, focus (2px outline), error (red border), disabled

### Cards
- Padding: 16-24px
- Variants: flat (border), elevated (shadow), interactive (hover state)

---

## 7. Accessibility

| Requirement | Value |
|-------------|-------|
| Touch targets | 44px × 44px minimum |
| Focus outline | 2px solid, 2px offset |
| Contrast (body) | 4.5:1 |
| Contrast (large) | 3:1 |

**Required:**
- Semantic HTML (`<button>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, not `<div onclick>`)
- Form labels for all inputs
- `aria-label` for icon-only buttons
- `aria-hidden="true"` for decorative icons
- `prefers-reduced-motion` support

---

## 8. Motion (Use tokens.css)

**APPROVED DURATIONS:**
```
100ms - hover, focus
200ms - buttons, inputs
300ms - modals, drawers
500ms - page transitions
```

**Easing:**
- `ease-out` - entrances
- `ease-in` - exits
- `ease-in-out` - state changes

**Only animate:** `transform`, `opacity` (avoid `width`, `height`, `margin`)

---

## 9. Responsive

**Breakpoints:**
```
640px  - tablet
768px  - tablet landscape
1024px - desktop
1280px - large desktop
```

**Mobile-first:** Start with mobile styles, enhance with `@media (min-width: ...)`.

---

## 10. Anti-AI Patterns (NEVER DO)

| ❌ Never | ✅ Instead |
|----------|-----------|
| Gradients everywhere | Solid colors, gradients sparingly |
| Random spacing (7px, 13px) | Use approved scale |
| Over-rounded corners (>16px) | 4px, 8px, 12px only |
| "Lorem ipsum" | Use sample-content.json |
| "John Doe", "Acme Corp" | Realistic names from sample-content.json |
| All text centered | Left-align body text |
| Rainbow colors (8+) | 2-3 accent colors max |
| No hover/focus states | Clear interactive feedback |
| Generate SVG code | Use icon libraries |

---

## Quick Checklist

Before finalizing:
- [ ] Spacing uses approved scale only
- [ ] Colors from tokens.css only
- [ ] Icons from library (no generated SVG)
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44px
- [ ] Focus states visible (2px outline)
- [ ] Contrast ≥ 4.5:1
- [ ] Semantic HTML
- [ ] Real content (no Lorem ipsum)
- [ ] Reduced motion support

